Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.05,0:05:39.51,Title,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(500,500)\pos(520,945)}英雄﹑二人
Comment: 0,0:01:08.20,0:01:08.20,Default,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.20,0:01:10.66,Default,,0,0,0,,連元素都算不上的人類
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.03,0:01:13.04,Default,,0,0,0,,接受我們的祝福吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.30,0:01:25.44,Default,,0,0,0,,去吧  一騎
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.72,0:01:27.49,Default,,0,0,0,,送日野美羽去龍宮島
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.84,0:01:30.37,Default,,0,0,0,,不要死啊  甲洋
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.14,0:01:34.95,Default,,0,0,0,,我已經多次失去肉體了  不會害怕了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.00,0:01:48.67,Default,,0,0,0,,這次  我一定要投影出你的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.44,0:02:07.14,Default,,0,0,0,,什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.26,0:02:15.19,Default,,0,0,0,,趕上了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.74,0:02:32.85,Default,,0,0,0,,你的故鄉就近在咫尺了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.92,0:02:36.27,Default,,0,0,0,,配合我的波長
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.93,0:02:51.08,Default,,0,0,0,,龍宮島
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.22,0:02:55.92,Default,,0,0,0,,馬里斯
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.75,0:03:02.44,Default,,0,0,0,,美羽
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.07,0:03:06.71,Default,,0,0,0,,不許再前進了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.18,0:03:07.98,Default,,0,0,0,,馬里斯
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.44,0:03:14.19,Default,,0,0,0,,少礙事
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.73,0:03:21.74,Default,,0,0,0,,機體已經把限制器解除了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.98,0:03:25.60,Default,,0,0,0,,看我用它阻止你們
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.52,0:03:27.22,Default,,0,0,0,,什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.95,0:03:29.62,Default,,0,0,0,,他打算讓機體停止
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.19,0:03:31.01,Default,,0,0,0,,快讓開
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.56,0:03:59.95,Default,,0,0,0,,睡吧  美羽
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.68,0:04:04.52,Default,,0,0,0,,馬里斯  住手…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.68,0:05:44.51,Default,,0,0,0,,和我的命令不一樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.27,0:05:48.06,Default,,0,0,0,,瑪萊斯貝洛
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.04,0:05:51.54,Default,,0,0,0,,請不要消滅我
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.91,0:05:52.61,Default,,0,0,0,,閉嘴
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.23,0:05:53.86,Default,,0,0,0,,住手
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.41,0:05:56.48,Default,,0,0,0,,我們會阻止美羽和Alvis
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.97,0:05:58.56,Default,,0,0,0,,牽牛星是你的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.33,0:06:00.02,Default,,0,0,0,,拜託了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.93,0:06:03.62,Default,,0,0,0,,你真是個怪人
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.90,0:06:07.23,Default,,0,0,0,,這是最後機會了  馬里斯
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.17,0:06:18.51,Default,,0,0,0,,這樣下去不是辦法
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.02,0:06:22.30,Default,,0,0,0,,顯示器擅自就…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.93,0:06:26.24,Default,,0,0,0,,是讓我去這裏嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.41,0:06:44.22,Default,,0,0,0,,這是
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.69,0:06:48.78,Default,,0,0,0,,推進器嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.48,0:06:52.19,Default,,0,0,0,,ArcheType Zero
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.25,0:07:09.56,Default,,0,0,0,,在生命消失前
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.89,0:07:11.49,Default,,0,0,0,,我要破壞你
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.56,0:07:16.29,Default,,0,0,0,,什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.82,0:07:25.46,Default,,0,0,0,,你就是我
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.16,0:07:27.94,Default,,0,0,0,,我就是你
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.67,0:07:40.61,Default,,0,0,0,,生命…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.83,0:07:43.81,Default,,0,0,0,,消失了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.39,0:07:48.49,Default,,0,0,0,,抱歉  賽蕾諾亞
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.40,0:07:57.15,Default,,0,0,0,,雷格特…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.01,0:07:59.78,Default,,0,0,0,,我不會讓你獨自上路的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.83,0:08:26.49,Default,,0,0,0,,怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.90,0:08:38.98,Default,,0,0,0,,快醒醒  美羽
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.50,0:08:40.86,Default,,0,0,0,,你也來幫忙
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.66,0:08:49.07,Default,,0,0,0,,看招
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.42,0:09:07.34,Default,,0,0,0,,知道萬害了嗎  馬里斯
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.77,0:09:09.85,Default,,0,0,0,,去吧  美羽
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.22,0:09:12.08,Default,,0,0,0,,敵人來了由我擋住
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.55,0:09:15.79,Default,,0,0,0,,去完成你說的必須要做的事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.62,0:09:18.11,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯  謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.14,0:09:20.51,Default,,0,0,0,,美羽會加油的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.57,0:09:30.65,Default,,0,0,0,,不可以
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.05,0:09:33.18,Default,,0,0,0,,不可以去
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.91,0:09:36.43,Default,,0,0,0,,不要去  美羽
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.16,0:09:39.28,Default,,0,0,0,,不要去啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.97,0:09:44.02,Default,,0,0,0,,不要為那些傢伙犧牲自己
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.58,0:09:52.36,Default,,0,0,0,,這是…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.82,0:10:02.62,Default,,0,0,0,,難道說  剛才那就是綁架我的理由嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.82,0:10:05.10,Default,,0,0,0,,我看到了未來
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.82,0:10:09.90,Default,,0,0,0,,美羽消失的未來
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.54,0:10:18.94,Default,,0,0,0,,就算與世界為敵
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.93,0:10:21.84,Default,,0,0,0,,我也…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.25,0:10:25.19,Default,,0,0,0,,決定要抹殺未來
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.46,0:10:36.64,Default,,0,0,0,,早說啊  笨蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.44,0:10:46.27,Default,,0,0,0,,歡迎回來  美羽
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.23,0:10:49.53,Default,,0,0,0,,那顆星星沉睡在這裏啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.90,0:10:51.84,Default,,0,0,0,,等等  美羽
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.36,0:10:53.48,Default,,0,0,0,,你打算做什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.19,0:10:56.38,Default,,0,0,0,,媽媽和艾米莉曾做過的事
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.83,0:10:59.98,Default,,0,0,0,,這個島也一直是這樣守護大家的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.61,0:11:01.71,Default,,0,0,0,,你明白…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.71,0:11:04.23,Default,,0,0,0,,總士  退下吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.32,0:11:07.64,Default,,0,0,0,,近藤先生  這算什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.06,0:11:11.06,Default,,0,0,0,,我們就是為了這種事而戰鬥的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.41,0:11:12.19,Default,,0,0,0,,總士
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.07,0:11:14.70,Default,,0,0,0,,我們別無選擇
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.09,0:11:17.80,Default,,0,0,0,,那是因為你們是笨蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.99,0:11:19.07,Default,,0,0,0,,快住手  總士
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.51,0:11:21.01,Default,,0,0,0,,這是美羽自願的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.20,0:11:22.66,Default,,0,0,0,,你只是被迫自願
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.71,0:11:26.09,Default,,0,0,0,,不許再接近了  總士
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.55,0:11:28.45,Default,,0,0,0,,我懂了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.04,0:11:31.49,Default,,0,0,0,,你是笨蛋裏最差的笨蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.10,0:11:34.43,Default,,0,0,0,,我果然沒法原諒你
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.85,0:11:47.24,Default,,0,0,0,,就算一開始別無選擇
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.98,0:11:50.90,Default,,0,0,0,,你要重複同樣的事到什麼時候
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.97,0:12:10.08,Default,,0,0,0,,戰鬥時給內心和平
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.66,0:12:13.53,Default,,0,0,0,,和平時保持戰鬥之心
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.84,0:12:21.39,Default,,0,0,0,,不躲在武器的影子裏
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.00,0:12:23.69,Default,,0,0,0,,正視對方的生命
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.79,0:13:03.59,Default,,0,0,0,,一騎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.13,0:13:43.39,Default,,0,0,0,,引導至未來吧  一騎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.33,0:13:48.06,Default,,0,0,0,,總士
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.77,0:14:11.18,Default,,0,0,0,,無論什麼力量
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.23,0:14:12.77,Default,,0,0,0,,總有一天都會歸於無
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.33,0:14:18.43,Default,,0,0,0,,你也會變成這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.71,0:14:33.71,Default,,0,0,0,,是我贏了 真壁一騎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.56,0:14:37.40,Default,,0,0,0,,終於迎來未來了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.70,0:14:40.18,Default,,0,0,0,,把我同化吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.92,0:14:44.65,Default,,0,0,0,,我的生命和力量也是你的  總士
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.46,0:14:46.96,Default,,0,0,0,,你究竟在說什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.02,0:14:57.92,Default,,0,0,0,,結果不是只知道犧牲自己或者別人嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.86,0:15:00.65,Default,,0,0,0,,誰稀罕你的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.08,0:15:02.95,Default,,0,0,0,,敢礙事我可不饒你
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.70,0:15:07.87,Default,,0,0,0,,總士才是  不要妨礙美羽
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.43,0:15:09.55,Default,,0,0,0,,我不會礙事的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.45,0:15:11.35,Default,,0,0,0,,一起去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.21,0:15:15.25,Default,,0,0,0,,總士  你打算做什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.61,0:15:18.20,Default,,0,0,0,,獻上自己並得到它
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.87,0:15:20.86,Default,,0,0,0,,你既然有這麼大的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.55,0:15:22.84,Default,,0,0,0,,我也有個想法
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.27,0:15:24.01,Default,,0,0,0,,想法？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.48,0:15:25.99,Default,,0,0,0,,你不同意我就自己去
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.77,0:15:28.46,Default,,0,0,0,,有本事就阻止我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.16,0:15:31.17,Default,,0,0,0,,我可是贏了真壁一騎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.38,0:15:32.90,Default,,0,0,0,,知道了  放開我
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.54,0:15:36.42,Default,,0,0,0,,可以吧  近藤先生
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.64,0:15:39.01,Default,,0,0,0,,允許你行動
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.55,0:15:41.47,Default,,0,0,0,,可是無可奈何的時候
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.82,0:15:44.23,Default,,0,0,0,,不要阻止美羽
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.91,0:15:51.48,Default,,0,0,0,,我已經不會再做虛假的夢了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.92,0:16:11.10,Default,,0,0,0,,還沒完
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.69,0:16:20.57,Default,,0,0,0,,里奈…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.52,0:16:29.51,Default,,0,0,0,,鏑木君
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.21,0:16:35.66,Default,,0,0,0,,結果還是失了嗎  馬里斯
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.48,0:16:41.88,Default,,0,0,0,,天照  用空白模式抑制同化現象
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.67,0:16:44.20,Default,,0,0,0,,海上形勢不利
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.29,0:16:47.02,Default,,0,0,0,,總士  美羽
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.75,0:16:49.38,Default,,0,0,0,,全都賭在你們身上了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.08,0:17:06.24,Default,,0,0,0,,美羽  已經不怕了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.10,0:17:09.94,Default,,0,0,0,,解除純粹Mir了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.41,0:17:11.95,Default,,0,0,0,,先被同化掉吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.20,0:17:14.28,Default,,0,0,0,,我再用憎恨來污染它
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.25,0:17:20.01,Default,,0,0,0,,最初的Mir和這個星球的生命化成一體而消失了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.26,0:17:23.74,Default,,0,0,0,,一定是有你這樣的存在
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.21,0:17:26.09,Default,,0,0,0,,和Mir一起進化了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.96,0:17:32.64,Default,,0,0,0,,總士
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.04,0:17:34.13,Default,,0,0,0,,別在意
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.51,0:17:36.82,Default,,0,0,0,,你是什麼人
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.12,0:17:38.35,Default,,0,0,0,,想要什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.63,0:17:40.58,Default,,0,0,0,,是什麼讓你成為你自己
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.36,0:17:44.77,Default,,0,0,0,,希望大家談談  不要再爭鬥了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.10,0:17:47.40,Default,,0,0,0,,想讓所有的悲傷事都到此為止
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.42,0:17:51.43,Default,,0,0,0,,那就得到那傢伙  由你去實現
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.38,0:17:57.17,Default,,0,0,0,,不對
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.63,0:17:59.56,Default,,0,0,0,,這孩子不是任何人的東西
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.09,0:18:07.15,Default,,0,0,0,,你在那裏嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.58,0:18:10.29,Default,,0,0,0,,美羽就在這裏
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.43,0:18:15.64,Default,,0,0,0,,救世主化
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.02,0:18:28.51,Default,,0,0,0,,空無一物的地平線彼端
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.16,0:18:32.29,Default,,0,0,0,,在那裏  有我們所不知道的未來
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.38,0:18:35.97,Default,,0,0,0,,你引導了未來呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.04,0:18:44.04,Default,,0,0,0,,等等  不要去  美羽
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.79,0:18:57.54,Default,,0,0,0,,那個
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.05,0:18:58.88,Default,,0,0,0,,美羽啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.52,0:19:00.32,Default,,0,0,0,,終於
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.15,0:19:02.48,Default,,0,0,0,,終於明了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.39,0:19:15.00,Default,,0,0,0,,美羽解除白紙的未來了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.64,0:19:17.23,Default,,0,0,0,,在終極的無的彼端
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.07,0:19:19.37,Default,,0,0,0,,正因為空無一物
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.57,0:19:21.31,Default,,0,0,0,,所以才充滿所有可能性的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.76,0:19:23.42,Default,,0,0,0,,可能性的地平線
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.93,0:19:26.69,Default,,0,0,0,,美羽
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.63,0:19:32.35,Default,,0,0,0,,美羽
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.88,0:19:37.84,Default,,0,0,0,,MK Sein
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.61,0:19:48.23,Default,,0,0,0,,美羽  沒事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.47,0:19:53.54,Default,,0,0,0,,美羽一直  想變成媽媽和艾米莉那樣
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.34,0:19:56.01,Default,,0,0,0,,就像別人告訴我的那樣
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.65,0:19:57.79,Default,,0,0,0,,一直一直
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.78,0:20:00.95,Default,,0,0,0,,認為那是對的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.97,0:20:04.13,Default,,0,0,0,,你就是你
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.66,0:20:07.96,Default,,0,0,0,,你會怎麼祝福世界
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.72,0:20:09.59,Default,,0,0,0,,讓我看看吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.82,0:20:15.46,Default,,0,0,0,,什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.18,0:20:17.42,Default,,0,0,0,,發生什麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.78,0:20:38.83,Default,,0,0,0,,沒用的  接受我們的祝福吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.89,0:21:06.85,Default,,0,0,0,,怎麼會…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.78,0:21:14.47,Default,,0,0,0,,停止吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.23,0:21:16.68,Default,,0,0,0,,不許再戰鬥了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.45,0:21:26.91,Default,,0,0,0,,上吧  Mk Sein
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.09,0:21:30.99,Default,,0,0,0,,美羽必須和他談談
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.99,0:21:32.92,Default,,0,0,0,,喂  美羽
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.68,0:21:38.67,Default,,0,0,0,,凱歐斯  牽牛星在那個容器裏
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.03,0:21:40.43,Default,,0,0,0,,破壞它搶過來
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.26,0:21:48.76,Default,,0,0,0,,人類竟敢搶我的東西
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.18,0:21:51.13,Default,,0,0,0,,那孩子不是任何人的東西
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.19,0:21:52.25,Default,,0,0,0,,你在說什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.72,0:21:58.07,Default,,0,0,0,,你就是我
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.90,0:22:00.11,Default,,0,0,0,,我就是你
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.64,0:22:02.67,Default,,0,0,0,,放開我
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.67,0:22:04.92,Default,,0,0,0,,悲傷的心情
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.64,0:22:06.74,Default,,0,0,0,,美羽也理解
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.34,0:22:11.90,Default,,0,0,0,,忘掉的事情  全都想起來也不要緊哦
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.60,0:22:14.88,Default,,0,0,0,,我連對話都不被允許
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.29,0:22:18.25,Default,,0,0,0,,憑你能懂什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.22,0:22:20.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Fenrir 啟動
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.19,0:22:29.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Fenrir 執行
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.57,0:22:39.23,Default,,0,0,0,,你幹什麼啊  美羽
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.13,0:22:44.70,Default,,0,0,0,,非常非常悲傷
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.85,0:22:53.61,Default,,0,0,0,,悲傷？
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.33,0:22:55.21,Default,,0,0,0,,它發怒了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.96,0:23:02.54,Default,,0,0,0,,先解決敵方救世主型
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.84,0:23:03.87,Default,,0,0,0,,兩人一起戰鬥
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.86,0:23:06.83,Default,,0,0,0,,美羽不喜歡動粗
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.98,0:23:08.74,Default,,0,0,0,,是對面先動粗的
Dialogue: 0,0:23:43.56,0:23:47.78,Default,,0,0,0,,消失吧
Dialogue: 0,0:24:05.57,0:24:07.53,Default,,0,0,0,,有本事阻止我的話
Dialogue: 0,0:24:08.15,0:24:09.49,Default,,0,0,0,,就試試看啊
Dialogue: 0,0:24:15.62,0:24:16.67,Default,,0,0,0,,不要拒絕
Dialogue: 0,0:24:17.11,0:24:18.67,Default,,0,0,0,,接受我們吧
Dialogue: 0,0:24:47.32,0:24:49.62,Default,,0,0,0,,接受祝福吧
Dialogue: 0,0:24:49.73,0:24:52.12,Default,,0,0,0,,這不是你的祝福
Dialogue: 0,0:25:07.34,0:25:11.18,Default,,0,0,0,,把那傢伙送進無吧
Dialogue: 0,0:25:43.13,0:25:44.84,Default,,0,0,0,,為什麼要射那邊
Dialogue: 0,0:25:45.45,0:25:47.29,Default,,0,0,0,,因為沒必要消滅那個人
Dialogue: 0,0:25:48.37,0:25:51.16,Default,,0,0,0,,他很痛苦  要給他最後一擊嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:25:51.59,0:25:55.46,Default,,0,0,0,,之所以痛苦  是因為沒法重生
Dialogue: 0,0:25:57.94,0:25:59.14,Default,,0,0,0,,來幫忙  總士
Dialogue: 0,0:26:00.42,0:26:01.66,Default,,0,0,0,,你想幹什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:26:02.98,0:26:04.39,Default,,0,0,0,,傳達給大家
Dialogue: 0,0:26:12.71,0:26:15.58,Default,,0,0,0,,這就是  美羽的祝福
Dialogue: 0,0:28:02.00,0:28:05.19,Default,,0,0,0,,下集  蒼穹的法芙娜  The Beyond
Dialogue: 0,0:28:05.61,0:28:08.67,Default,,0,0,0,,最終集  蒼穹的彼端
